quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  48,1,We have opened up a clear victory for you
  48,2,"so God may forgive you for any offence of yours you have committed previously or whatever you may do later on, complete His favor toward you and guide you along a Straight Road"
  48,3,and so God may support you in a mighty success
  48,4,"He is the One Who sends down Serenity on believersÂ´ hearts s they may add faith to the faith they already have. God [commands] the armies of Heaven and Earth; God is Aware, Wise"
  48,5,"so that He may admit believing men and believing women into gardens through which rivers flow, to live there forever, and to cancel out their evil deeds for them. That will be a supreme Achievement with God"
  48,6,"so He may punish hypocritical men and women as well as associating men and women who conjecture such evil about God; on them will fall an evil turn of fortune. God has become angry with them, and has cursed them and prepared Hell for them. How evil is such a goal"
  48,7,"God [commands] the armies of Heaven and Earth. God is Powerful Wise"
  48,8,"We have sent you as a witness, herald and warner"
  48,9,"so you may (all) believe in God and His messenger, and revere and honor Him, and glorify Him morning and evening"